metadata.description: 2222glassfaces is many things at once. One artist, 2222 AI-generated images of that artist - magazine photos, fan art, paparazzi photos, images of alternate versions of Glassface. The goal is to spread these images far and wide, as an experiment in creating an artificial public record / memory of Glassface.
